CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. A10, reads: "$100 for the YWCA - So-Re-Lit Juniors gave a check for $100 to the YWCA in memory of the late Mrs. Emmett Davis, a staunch community worker. The presentation was made at the reception given at the Greene Hearthe [Hearth] by the group.  Left to right: Mrs. Aline Herd, Mrs. Ora Ware, Mrs. William J. McKee, receiving the check, and Mrs. Nan Lewis. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait members of So-Re-Lit Juniors, including Aline Herd seated second from left, Mrs. Ora Ware third from left, and Nan Lewis fourth from left, posed in Greene Hearth
